comment: /**  * This is how the IDs were formed in v5.4  */
code: /**  * This is how the IDs were formed in v5.4  */ public static final String v54DocumentId(String jobId, String snapshotId, int docNum) {     return jobId + "-" + snapshotId + "#" + docNum. }

comment: /**  * Given the id of a state document it extracts the job id  * @param docId the state document id  * @return the job id or {@code null} if the id is not valid  */
code: /**  * Given the id of a state document it extracts the job id  * @param docId the state document id  * @return the job id or {@code null} if the id is not valid  */ public static final String extractJobId(String docId) {     int suffixIndex = docId.lastIndexOf("_" + TYPE + "_").     return suffixIndex <= 0 ? null : docId.substring(0, suffixIndex). }
